      "title": "Clearan Flow ",
      "description": "Clearance Flow is a production-ready, full-stack web application designed to digitize and automate the traditional student clearance process in universities. Previously, students had to manually visit multiple departments (including Finance, Library, Hostel, Transport, and Academic offices) to collect signatures—a process prone to delays and errors. Clearance Flow replaces this manual workflow with a centralized, role-based platform where students submit requests, track their real-time department-by-department status, and receive automated clearance certificates. Department officers and administrators use custom dashboards to review documents, add remarks, and approve requests instantly. The platform integrates real-time communications, document verification, email automation, and detailed data analytics to provide a seamless administrative experience.",
